{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109402731579-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109402731579-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100130081636-1","P_10100130081636-2","P_10100130081636-3","P_10100130081636-4"],"books":null,"booksNew":[{"seriesId":"BKC_10100000002119","bookId":"BK_10100000005225","unitId":null,"lessonId":null,"sectionId":null,"termType":1,"classLevel":4}],"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":5,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":67,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>母亲的珠宝</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">在几百年前的罗马城，两个孩子正在清晨的阳光下快乐地玩耍，他们的母亲康妮黎亚走过来对他们说：“亲爱的孩子，今天有一位富有的朋友要来我们家做客，她还会向我们展示她的珠宝。”   </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">下午，那个富有的朋友来了。金环在她的手臂上闪烁着耀眼的光芒，手指上的戒指闪闪发光，脖子上挂着金项链，发髻上的珍珠饰品折射出柔和的光。                                       兄弟俩羡慕地看着客人，又看看自己的母亲。母亲只穿了一件素的外套，身上没有任何珍贵的饰品。但是她和善的笑容却照亮了她的脸庞，远胜于任何宝石的光芒。她金棕色的头发编成了一条长长的辫子，盘绕在头上像一顶皇冠。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“你们想看看我其他的珠宝吗？”富有的女人问。                                         她的仆人拿来一只盒子并放在桌子上。这位女士打开盒子，里头有成堆的像血一样红的红宝石，像天一样蓝的蓝宝石，像海一样碧绿的翡翠，像阳光一样耀眼的钻石。                          这对兄弟呆呆地看着这些珠宝：“要是我们的母亲能够拥有这些东西该多好啊！”             客人炫耀完自己的珠宝之后，自满而又怜悯地说：“告诉我，康<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">妮</span>黎亚，你真的这么穷吗？什么珠宝都没有吗？”  </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">康妮黎亚坦然地笑道：“不，我当然有珠宝，我的珠宝比你的更贵重。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">客人睁大眼睛“是吗？快拿来让我看看吧！”                                             母亲拉过两个男孩儿：“这就是我的珠宝！”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">特贝瑞斯和卡尔斯永远不会忘记他们母亲当时脸上骄傲的表情以及深深的爱意。数年后，他们成为罗马伟大的政治家，但他们仍然常常忆起当年的这一幕。</span></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"兄弟俩在看到富人展示的珠宝和得知了母亲的珠宝后，心理经历了怎样的变化？","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"从对富人的羡慕，到对母亲的不满。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"从羡慕富人的珠宝，希望母亲也能拥有这些；到被母亲的话语所震撼和感动。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"从对富人的羡慕；到对母亲质朴形象的欣赏和赞美。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"从羡慕富人的珠宝；到对富人傲慢话语的不满。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"康妮黎亚拥有的珠宝是什么？","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"她引以为傲的两个孩子。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"她善良、质朴的品格。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"她和善的笑容和金棕色的头发。","file"